{"tid":837111,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"已報警：前幾日同人講中秋快樂無啦啦比人打","createTime":"2018-09-26T06:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T14:02:41.000Z","uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43d8fb44f45fb737c45c9bb93cc9a02b81fe1ade","tid":837111,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"好撚忟<br />\n滑雪前幾日中秋節前夕同frd食飯<br />\n食撚完飯坐低吹水<br />\n等到十二點一到 我懶熱情咁攬住個frd講中秋快樂<br />\n然後佢無啦啦一拳中埋黎 然後係咁打鳩我<br />\n我成個人呆撚左 d鹼水糉係個口跌晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後我捉鳩住佢衫領問佢做乜打我<br />\n然後佢講左句中完再揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻屌鳩佢咁中意同人隻揪就死上去力威啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後條戇鳩仔可能知驚即刻跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後追撚左佢幾條帶再捉佢上警署備案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講聲中秋快樂無啦啦比人打 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25fc40331a187bff38eb297239e6657880e73b1","tid":837111,"uid":75500,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"6a6978be63e03af66b839032672bcd492c61d652","tid":837111,"uid":176063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afbbff43143675942d9d1c09efc0e01c3eab09b6","tid":837111,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:46:27.000Z","msg":"有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 